    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Patient:

          1. has an CardioMEMs device implanted

          2. has been diagnosed with various stages of heart failure as described by New York Heart
             Association (NYHA)

          3. is able to give informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

        Patient:

          1. has pacemaker/ICD

          2. is pregnant or breastfeeding

          3. is an amputee

          4. has been diagnosed with multiple medical conditions that would make participation
             burdensome

          5. not able to co-operate with impedance measurements
      </textblock>
